I'm sorry.

00:03:31.250 --> 00:03:32.969
I can't talk to you today.

00:03:32.969 --> 00:03:37.650
I just lost my mother, and I'm meeting with the funeral director this afternoon.

00:03:37.650 --> 00:03:38.650
I'm sorry.

