00:04:39.670 --> 00:04:45.310
If you're reading a scripture, try to express the feelings indicated in the passage, but

00:04:45.310 --> 00:04:49.910
don't draw undue attention to yourself.

00:04:49.910 --> 00:04:57.269
So by thinking about your listeners, choosing your words carefully, and showing your interest,

00:04:57.269 --> 00:05:01.709
you'll refresh, comfort, and invigorate your listeners.
